Ouch, it hurts. Mother, I know.

58
00:03:20,670 --> 00:03:22,350
Are you done? Hurry up and go.

59
00:03:22,749 --> 00:03:24,990
Seeing your vigorous health,

60
00:03:24,990 --> 00:03:26,429
- we are very glad.
- We're leaving now.

61
00:03:26,510 --> 00:03:27,350
Yao Wen, Yao Wu.

62
00:03:28,189 --> 00:03:30,189
The door is over here.
Let me take you out.

63
00:03:38,790 --> 00:03:40,029
